Interface IEDIF300Listener

This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by EDIF300Parser.

Namespace: GCore.Antlr.Grammers.Edif300
Assembly: Edif300.dll
Syntax
public interface IEDIF300Listener : Antlr4.Runtime.Tree.IParseTreeListener
